* [[Amadeus_Austrian_Music_Award|Amadeus Austrian Music Award]] 2005 for "Best Pop/Rock national" and "Best Single national"
* [[ECHO_(music_award)|ECHO]] 2006 for "Best National Female Artist (Rock/Pop)"
* [[Amadeus_Austrian_Music_Award|Amadeus Austrian Music Award]] 2006 for "Best Pop/Rock national" and "Best Single national"
